    "description": "<strong>THIS GAME IS DESIGNED TO BE ENJOYED FOR ABOUT 20 MINUTES</strong><br><br>Chase Fox's third game.<br><br>One whodunnit mystery. Five phantom thieves.<br><br>The Great Artists is a tiny fantasy comedy mystery game that tells a short story about an incident involving five phantom thieves at an art museum.<br><br>Observe a 10-minute mystery story about light-constructed snakes, incredibly rare fishes that can swim without water, many voguish rose-colored clothes, cards that obey no laws of modern physics and artistic light structures. <br><br>Move the camera, stop time, jump between specific times, experience the story and solve mysteries the way you wanted.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249730/extras/a2e7d84adf9cfd2fb7cade3d33571184.poster.avif?t=1691820555\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249730/extras/a2e7d84adf9cfd2fb7cade3d33571184.webm?t=1691820555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249730/extras/a2e7d84adf9cfd2fb7cade3d33571184.mp4?t=1691820555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249730/extras/e309402de0bfcb93617f6fccc1f1fc16.poster.avif?t=1691820555\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249730/extras/e309402de0bfcb93617f6fccc1f1fc16.webm?t=1691820555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249730/extras/e309402de0bfcb93617f6fccc1f1fc16.mp4?t=1691820555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autop